        <trans-unit id="104" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>The event interface that you use to fire COM events must be a COM interface.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="105" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>In this situation, the interface should either be defined using a Visual C++ attribute, or imported using <bpt id="p1">[</bpt>#import<ept id="p1">](../../preprocessor/hash-import-directive-cpp.md)</ept> from a type library with #import's embedded_idl attribute.</source>
